title: Bodybuilding - Leroy Colbert and Nikki Fuller - Interview (uncut
description:
Okay, this is the uncut interview done with Leroy Colbert and Nikki Fuller.  

Leroy Colbert (first man to have over 21" arms) and, FBB pro Nikki Fuller are the two people in this video.  As far as I can tell it was done in the last few years but, have yet to find an exact date.

The runtime is 75 mins (1hr15mins) and, is a good little find.  I do find the video cut quicckly at the end but, those who I've talked to say that is how it was done (not sure why, maybe sloppy editing by the filming crew) or, since this is the uncut version, it's the raw and uneditted video (that is what I can figure out)

More videos to come, please help seed
